<p>Doctors and observers say a drone strike by Sudan’s Rapid Support Forces (RSF) hit a vehicle carrying displaced families near Er Rahad in North Kordofan on Saturday, killing at least 24 people — including eight children and two infants — according to the Sudan Doctors Network and multiple news reports. The doctors’ group said the passengers were fleeing fighting when the attack happened.</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/po7yY4LZySbbkn9Gfaze8pxcB_YIaqEienmbLUwsM2ia5KukPG3pToUFjgbrhKjp815u8UvRgvxg2kYGcKpf_2X2Y5Y9RFbAT9t53DLj7zPclAGRFk9G1FlLRjNHL5MRZdhJvezn6ykredNcwF9u7herqk2uXalwN4utyTt7G5GnJlX16OCkB8_vyYFMFqBktt1u3wT2NxR8xyDbCJianQz51LZ3SPd0uGrkeTmAAtpbBVw' alt='Displaced people in Sudan, as fighting drives families from their homes.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Where they were coming from: The Sudan Doctors Network said the passengers had fled fighting in the Dubeiker area before the strike near Er Rahad.</li><li>Who is reporting it: The Sudan Doctors Network, which tracks incidents in the war, described the attack near Er Rahad in North Kordofan.</li><li>Aid risks: DW tied the reported strike to rising dangers for relief operations, noting it followed a reported attack on a UN World Food Program convoy the day before.</li><li>How responsibility is described: Coverage cited the doctors’ group and observers as blaming the RSF for the drone strike.</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Sudan Doctors Network: The group said an RSF drone strike hit a vehicle carrying displaced families near Er Rahad, and that the passengers had fled fighting in the Dubeiker area. (<a href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2026/feb/07/sudan-rsf-drone-attack-rahad-kills-displaced-people'>The Guardian</a>)</li><li>Observers cited by DW: DW said observers blamed the RSF for the strike and pointed to broader risks for humanitarian operations, noting it came a day after a reported attack on a UN World Food Program convoy. (<a href='https://www.dw.com/en/sudan-suspected-rsf-drone-attack-on-aid-convoy-kills-dozens/a-75855616'>Deutsche Welle</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2026/feb/07/sudan-rsf-drone-attack-rahad-kills-displaced-people'>RSF drone attack kills 24 people fleeing fighting in central Sudan, says doctors group</a> - theguardian.com</li><li><a href='https://www.dw.com/en/sudan-suspected-rsf-drone-attack-on-aid-convoy-kills-dozens/a-75855616'>Sudan: Suspected RSF drone attack on aid convoy kills dozens</a> - dw.com</li><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/24-killed-in-drone-attack-by-paramilitary-group-in-sudan-10966206#publisher=newsstand'>24 Killed In Drone Attack By Paramilitary Group In Sudan</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='https://www.pbs.org/newshour/world/drone-attack-by-paramilitary-group-in-sudan-kills-24-including-8-children'>Drone attack by paramilitary group in Sudan kills 24, including 8 children</a> - pbs.org</li><li><a href='https://www.ctvnews.ca/world/article/drone-attack-by-paramilitary-group-in-sudan-kills-24-including-8-children-doctors-group-says/'>At least 24 people are killed, including eight children, in a drone strike by the Rapid Support Forces on a vehicle carrying displaced families near Er Rahad, North Kordofan, Sudan.</a> - ctvnews.ca</li></ul>